cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.MM

The paper deals with image classification using machine learning techniques, specifically for breast cancer histopathology images. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves unsupervised learning, which suggests that it could belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the use of neural networks and support vector machines indicates that it could belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also involves data analysis and mining, which suggests that it could belong to cs.IR (Information Retrieval) or cs.MM (Multimedia).
